Others think that there's a humanitarian need to understand the disorders to help people. So as you think about these two sort of perspectives, you can think that when people behaved very unusually-- I'll show you a picture of this that we think some time ago that people would literally trephinate, that is, make a hole in the skull of individuals to attempt to let out the demons. That was the interpretation of the time.
