More recently there's a best seller, couple years ago about checklists. So this is what's done in emergency rooms. And you may know that there's an unfortunately high rate of errors in hospitals, even among highly skilled physicians in the best of academic hospitals. There's just miscommunications between doctors and nurses, changes of shifts, and so on. Mistakes happen.
